    <content>&lt;P&gt;The standard solution using SAP Cloud ALM is&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://support.sap.com/en/alm/sap-cloud-alm/operations/expert-portal/real-user-monitoring/real-user-monitoring-content.html?anchorId=section" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Real User Monitoring&lt;/A&gt;. Unfortunately right now no content for Build Work Zone is availalbe. But you could start with the content for Cloud Foundry and standalone UI5 apps.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
